{"tid":2221793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳凱欣失議席 終院頒佈書面判辭","createTime":"2020-09-28T15:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T16:34:25.000Z","uid":365024,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7951aa61e35ea238971f8b4cad0186c0714de602","tid":2221793,"uid":365024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T15:29:10.000Z","msg":"2016 年因立法會宣誓事件遭褫奪議員資格的劉小麗，於 2018 年參加九龍西立法會補選時，被選舉主任裁定提名無效。高院早前裁定劉小麗選舉呈請勝訴，及於補選中勝出的陳凱欣「非妥為當選」，陳凱欣其後向終審法院提出上訴，本月 18 日遭終院拒絕，陳凱欣即時喪失議席。終院今（28日）頒布書面原因，指選舉主任沒有給予劉小麗解釋機會，屬程序不公及不符法例要求，此舉不但影響參選人的基本政治權利，亦影響公眾對整個選舉過程的信心，認為原審決定正確。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%99%B3%E5%87%B1%E6%AC%A3%E5%A4%B1%E8%AD%B0%E5%B8%AD-%E7%B5%82%E9%99%A2%E5%88%A4%E8%BE%AD-%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%BB%E4%B8%8D%E4%BA%88%E5%8A%89%E5%B0%8F%E9%BA%97%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%8B%E5%B1%AC%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%AC-%E6%AF%8B%E9%A0%88%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E5%85%B6%E5%AE%A3%E8%AA%93%E7%9C%9F%E5%AF%A6%E6%84%8F%E5%9C%96/?fbclid=IwAR0f8DYiFmW8m0R7sI7FCBSxLC5h3wE6rEbKbpN3jUlFyoz8MsE2gSmfBHY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2587%25B1%25E6%25AC%25A3%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%25B8%25AD-%25E7%25B5%2582%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%2588%25A4%25E8%25BE%25AD-%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25BA%2588%25E5%258A%2589%25E5%25B0%258F%25E9%25BA%2597%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E9%2587%258B%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E7%25A8%258B%25E5%25BA%258F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2585%25AC-%25E6%25AF%258B%25E9%25A0%2588%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%2585%25B6%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E8%25AA%2593%25E7%259C%259F%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%259C%2596%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0f8DYiFmW8m0R7sI7FCBSxLC5h3wE6rEbKbpN3jUlFyoz8MsE2gSmfBHY&d=Wx0cKZaQlto0GELw8F4hIcv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=1fc7fee4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2587%25B1%25E6%25AC%25A3%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%25B8%25AD-%25E7%25B5%2582%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%2588%25A4%25E8%25BE%25AD-%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25BA%2588%25E5%258A%2589%25E5%25B0%258F%25E9%25BA%2597%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E9%2587%258B%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E7%25A8%258B%25E5%25BA%258F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2585%25AC-%25E6%25AF%258B%25E9%25A0%2588%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%2585%25B6%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E8%25AA%2593%25E7%259C%259F%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%259C%2596%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0f8DYiFmW8m0R7sI7FCBSxLC5h3wE6rEbKbpN3jUlFyoz8MsE2gSmfBHY&h=d5e49385\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%99%B3%E5%87%B1%E6%AC%A3%E5%A4%B1%E8%AD%B0%E5%B8%AD-%E7%B5%82%E9%99%A2%E5%88%A4%E8%BE%AD-%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%BB%E4%B8%8D%E4%BA%88%E5%8A%89%E5%B0%8F%E9%BA%97%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%8B%E5%B1%AC%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%AC-%E6%AF%8B%E9%A0%88%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E5%85%B6%E5%AE%A3%E8%AA%93%E7%9C%9F%E5%AF%A6%E6%84%8F%E5%9C%96/?fbclid=IwAR0f8DYiFmW8m0R7sI7FCBSxLC5h3wE6rEbKbpN3jUlFyoz8MsE2gSmfBHY</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>Mr Justice Cheung PJ:<br />\n<span class=\"small\">8.  </span>In essence, it was contended that the judge was right to regard whether the Returning Officer&rsquo;s conclusion that Ms Lau lacked the requisite intention to uphold the Basic Law and pledge allegiance to the HKSAR was correct despite the procedural irregularity was a relevant consideration in deciding whether a &ldquo;material&rdquo; irregularity had occurred. However, he erred in considering that it was not necessary to determine the point when deciding whether there was a material irregularity, because the important right of Ms Lau to stand for election protected under article 26 of the Basic Law and article 21(b) of the Hong Kong Bill of Rights, and the rules of natural justice had been breached in this case.<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/ju/ju_frame.jsp?DIS=131081&amp;currpage=T\" dat